|---|---|---|
| `ticket-checkout` | Stripe Checkout Session + atomic qty_pending increment | `STRIPE_SECRET_KEY` ‚úÖ |
| `ticket-payment-webhook` | Stripe sig verify ‚Üí finalize order + flip attendees ‚Üí active | `STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET` ‚úÖ |
| `event-staff-link-generator` | JWT mint/revoke for staff check-in | `STAFF_LINK_SECRET` ‚úÖ |
