## 2026-05-05 ‚Äî Landlord V1 launch blockers cleared (7 fixes)

**Commit:** `f932692` | **Branch:** `fix/landlord-launch-blockers`

### What shipped

#### `ThreePanelLayout.tsx` ‚Äî CJS shim removed (L1)
- Replaced `export const usePanelContext = () => { require(...) }` (broke in Vite ESM, caused blank-page crash on all routes) with clean ES re-export: `export { useThreePanelContext as usePanelContext }`

#### `useAuth.tsx` ‚Äî Landlord account type + PostHog (L2)
- Added `AccountType = "renter" | "landlord"` + `SignUpOptions` interface
- `signUp` passes `emailRedirectTo` ‚Üí `/host/onboarding` for landlords, stores `account_type` in `user_metadata`
- `signInWithGoogle` accepts `redirectTo` + `options`, routes landlords to `/host/onboarding`
- PostHog `identifyUser` on `SIGNED_IN` / `TOKEN_REFRESHED`; `resetPostHog` on `SIGNED_OUT`

#### `ApartmentDetail.tsx` ‚Äî Price format + HostCard (L3)
- Monthly price now uses `formatListingPrice()` ‚Üí `$3.800.000 COP` / `$450 USD` (was raw `toLocaleString`)
- Weekly/daily price tiles hidden when `null` instead of always showing `$N/A`
- `<HostCard landlordId={...} />` renders when `apartment.landlord_id` present; falls back to legacy host_name card

#### `Login.tsx` ‚Äî Smart post-login routing (L4)
- Reads `?returnTo=` query param (set by `HeroChatPrompt.savePendingPrompt`) with open-redirect guard
- On success without explicit `returnTo`: fetches `account_type` metadata ‚Üí landlord ‚Üí `/host/dashboard`, renter ‚Üí `/`
- `signInWithGoogle` passes `explicitReturn` so OAuth callback lands on correct page

#### `Onboarding.tsx` ‚Äî Landlord bypass (L5)
- Added guard: if `user_metadata.account_type === "landlord"` ‚Üí `<Navigate to="/host/onboarding" replace />`

#### `Signup.tsx` ‚Äî 3-step landlord-aware flow (L6)
- Step 1: `AccountTypeStep` ‚Äî renter vs. landlord card picker
- Step 2: Email/password form with landlord-specific copy ("List your space")
- Step 3: Inline success surface (`signupComplete` state) instead of navigate-to-/login redirect
- Passes `accountType` to `signUp()` so metadata + redirect are set correctly

#### `index.html` ‚Äî Debug script cleanup (L7)
- Removed temporary `window.__errors = []` error-capture script added during diagnostic session

### Root cause resolved: split-module AuthContext crash
The blank-page crash affecting all routes was caused by Vite's browser HTTP cache serving the old `useAuth.tsx?t=<timestamp>` module alongside the fresh server version. `AuthProvider` used the new `AuthContext` while downstream components read from the old one ‚Üí `useContext()` returned `undefined` ‚Üí throw. Fixed by clearing `node_modules/.vite` + fresh server start.

### Gates

| Gate | Result |
|---|---|
| Preview smoke test | ‚úÖ `/apartments/:id` renders price, HostCard, MobileNav ‚Äî no errors |
| Build | ‚úÖ Clean |
| Vite cache cleared | ‚úÖ `node_modules/.vite` removed before commit |

### Open (L8 + landlord V1 remainders)
| Priority | Item |
|---|---|
| üî¥ | L8: Listing wizard Step 1 "Continue" stuck disabled when Places autocomplete returns no suggestions |
