## 2026-05-03 ‚Äî Phase 1 EVENTS backend (6/10 P0 launch-blocker tasks shipped) + Gemini SDK migration

Six events tasks landed and were verified against the live Supabase project (`zkwcbyxiwklihegjhuql`). All four edge functions deployed, all RPCs smoke-tested via SQL, every boundary test green. Plus the Gemini native SDK migration (045) + skill housekeeping (046) that unlocks tool combination + Maps grounding for the Phase 2-4 AI work.

### What shipped (in build order)

**001 event-schema-migration** ([supabase/migrations/20260503011925_event_phase1.sql](supabase/migrations/20260503011925_event_phase1.sql))
- ALTER `events` + 5 NEW tables (`event_venues`, `event_tickets`, `event_orders`, `event_attendees`, `event_check_ins`) + 10 RPCs
- Audit #3 fix: `qty_pending` column with `CHECK (qty_sold + qty_pending <= qty_total)`
- Search-path hardening migration shipped same day ‚Üí 9 advisor warnings dropped (94 ‚Üí 84)
- 1 venue + 1 published event + 4 tickets + 2 orders + 3 attendees + 2 check-ins seeded for QA

**002 host-event-new-wizard** ([src/pages/host/HostEventNew.tsx](src/pages/host/HostEventNew.tsx) + 8 wizard files)
- 4-step wizard (Basics ‚Üí Tickets ‚Üí Review ‚Üí Publish) with `useEventDraft` autosave hook
- Build green, lint clean, route added at `/host/event/new`

**045 gemini-native-sdk-migration** ([supabase/functions/_shared/gemini.ts](supabase/functions/_shared/gemini.ts))
- Rewrote `_shared/gemini.ts` from OpenAI-compat fetch ‚Üí native `npm:@google/genai@^1.0.0` SDK
- New helpers: `callGeminiStructured<T>`, `callGeminiAgent`, `withRetry`, `geminiClient()`
- G1 (responseJsonSchema required) enforced at type level
- G2 enforced by signature: no `temperature` parameter accepted
