- Legacy `fetchGemini`/`fetchGeminiStream` retained for ai-chat (1054 lines, deferred to follow-up PR per task 045 spec)
- Verification: lint baseline preserved, build 4.55s, **170 tests pass**

**046 gemini-skill-housekeeping** ([.claude/skills/gemini/SKILL.md](.claude/skills/gemini/SKILL.md) + 3 reference files)
- Patched line 387: replaced "tool combination NOT supported in Gemini 3" ‚Üí verbatim live-doc note about `include_server_side_tool_invocations: true` + thoughtSignature preservation
