- Map pin click now opens a Google Maps InfoWindow with a peek (photo + title + neighborhood/BR/BA + price/rating + "View details ‚Üí" button) instead of immediately navigating away. Preserves the chat session ‚Äî anon users don't lose their conversation just to peek a listing.
