## 2026-04-23 (Week 2 Mon/Tue + CORS fix + PR #1 merged to main)

### Shipped to production
- **PR #1 merged** ‚Üí commit `287b1cc` ‚Üí Vercel deploy on `main` ‚Üí **`www.mdeai.co` now serves the chat-central canvas** (was the old `Index` marketing page). Verified: production bundle contains `ChatCanvas`, `apartment_save_counts` RPC name, "What are you looking for" welcome headline, "Ask about rentals" placeholder. End-to-end POST from `Origin: https://www.mdeai.co` returns 200 streaming SSE with 10 Laureles listings + phase events.

### `fix(cors)` ‚Äî unblocks every browser POST to edge functions
- **`supabase/functions/_shared/http.ts`** ‚Äî `getCorsHeaders(req)` was missing `Access-Control-Allow-Methods`. Browsers send `OPTIONS` preflight with `Access-Control-Request-Method: POST`, see no `Allow-Methods` in response, silently abort the follow-up POST. Server logs showed `OPTIONS 204` with no matching POST ‚Äî every anon chat send failed with "Failed to get response."
- Added `Access-Control-Allow-Methods: POST, GET, OPTIONS`, added `x-anon-session-id` to `Allow-Headers` (so the 3-msg anon gate doesn't trip a second preflight failure), added `Access-Control-Max-Age: 86400` + `Vary: Origin` for Cloudflare/browser cache correctness.
- **All 10 edge functions redeployed** on `zkwcbyxiwklihegjhuql` (ai-chat, rentals, ai-router, ai-search, ai-trip-planner, ai-optimize-route, ai-suggest-collections, google-directions, rules-engine, p1-crm).

### Week 2 Tue ‚Äî save + add-to-trip + social proof
