- **`src/hooks/useChatActions.ts`** ‚Äî owns `savedIds`, `saveCounts`, `trips`; exposes `toggleSave` (optimistic w/ rollback), `addToTrip`, `createTripAndAdd`, `fetchSaveCounts`. Anon users get a friendly sign-in toast instead of RLS errors.
