## 2026-04-05 (Security Hardening Session)

### Security Fixes (4 CRITICAL resolved)
- **verify_jwt = true** on all 10 edge functions (was false on 9/10) ‚Üí `supabase/config.toml`
- **CORS locked down** ‚Üí `_shared/http.ts` rewritten with `getCorsHeaders(req)` and allowed origins list (mdeai.co, medell-n-connect.vercel.app, localhost:8080); wildcard `*` eliminated
- **Service role key pattern fixed** ‚Üí new `_shared/supabase-clients.ts` with `getUserClient()` (anon key + JWT) and `getServiceClient()` (admin only); applied to ai-search + ai-router
- **Gemini timeout helper** ‚Üí new `_shared/gemini.ts` with 30s `AbortController`; ready for all functions
- **Frontend hardcoded secrets removed** ‚Üí 7 files: all `zkwcbyxiwklihegjhuql` URLs ‚Üí `import.meta.env.VITE_SUPABASE_URL`; 3 files: JWT tokens ‚Üí `import.meta.env.VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY`
- **Dead code removed** ‚Üí `useIntentRouter.ts` (orphaned) + `ChatRightPanel.tsx` (orphaned) deleted
- **Wasted AI call removed** ‚Üí `useChat.ts` no longer calls ai-router on every message (result was computed but never used; saves ~50% Gemini cost per message)

